    "name": "HT-CentralCashPool-CLM-Mirror-TimeEpoch-BiWeekly-10",
    "_postman_id": "ht-v14-8m-pool-alloc-breach",
    "description": "HT v14 — $8M Pool, Allocation Breach + Spot Sell Trigger\n\n  CHANGES FROM v13:\n  1. Initial cash pool raised from $3M to $8M.\n     CASH-PAM-3M: NP=$8,000,000, discount=-$8,000,000, IED=Feb-28.\n\n  2. BTC allocation bands narrowed to match $8M portfolio reality:\n     min=20%, target=25%, max=30%\n     Rationale:\n       Pre-deployment (Feb-28):  0 BTC → alloc = 0%\n       After CLM-Lending IED:    20 BTC×$50K = $1M / $8M = 12.5%\n       After CLM-SpotTrade IED:  40 BTC×$50K = $2M / $8M = 25.0%  ← at target\n       Mar-15 ($52K):  2.08M / 8.09M = 25.7%  ← rising\n       Mar-31 ($55K):  2.20M / 8.21M = 26.8%  ← rising\n       Apr-15 ($58K):  2.32M / 8.33M = 27.8%  ← rising\n       Apr-30 ($62K):  2.48M / 8.49M = 29.2%  ← approaching 30%\n       May-15 ($68K):  2.72M / 8.73M = 31.2%  ← BREACH → SELL FIRES\n       After sell:     alloc returns to 25% target\n\n  3. Mirror model initialNotionalPrincipal updated to $8,000,000.\n\n  4. PORTFOLIO_NAV_01 recalculated: NAV = 40×BTC_price + $6,011,887\n     ($6,011,887 = $1M T-Bills at face + $5,011,887 cash residual after deployments)\n\n  5. LiquidityBuffer thresholds scaled: min=$150K, target=$300K.\n\n  6. OUTFLOWS_01 ops base scaled for $8M portfolio in derive script.\n\n  T-BILL LADDER (unchanged):\n    TBILL-3mo-400K: $400K face, MD=Jun-01, discount=$3,680\n    TBILL-4mo-350K: $350K face, MD=Jul-01, discount=$4,321\n    TBILL-5mo-250K: $250K face, MD=Aug-01, discount=$3,886\n    Total purchase: $988,113  |  Residual in pool: $5,011,887\n\n  ALLOCATION NARRATIVE:\n    Feb-28  CASH-PAM IED    → pool $8M established, BTC alloc = 0%\n    Mar-01  CLM×2 IEDs      → $1M+$1M deployed, 40 BTC, alloc = 25%\n    Mar→Apr                 → BTC rises, alloc drifts 25%→29%\n    May-15  BREACH 30%      → ad_btc01_spot fires SELL signal\n                               CLM-SpotTrade PP reduces NP, cash returned\n                               alloc trimmed back toward 25% target\n    May→Aug                 → stable, T-Bill ladder unwinds Jun/Jul/Aug\n\n  STEPS: 11  SCENARIO: ht_v14_8m_pool_scn01  CONTRACTS: 6",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
